ingual strings\n88:   - Add: `identity.description` with multilingual strings\n89:   - Add: `identity.icon: icon.png`\n90:   - Verify: All identity fields present\n91: \n92: - [ ] **T3.3** List associated tools\n93:   - Add: `tools: [tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml]`\n94:   - Verify: Tool path listed\n95: \n96: - [ ] **T3.4** Configure Python source entry\n97:   - Add: `extra.python.source: provider/agentcube.py`\n98:   - Verify: Source path points to provider implementation\n99: \n100: ---\n101: \n102: ## Phase 4: Tool Parameter Schema (tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml)\n103: \n104: - [ ] **T4.1** Create tools directory structure\n105:   - Directory: `integrations/dify-plugin/tools/`\n106:   - Verify: Directory exists\n107: \n108: - [ ] **T4.2** Define tool identity\n109:   - File: `integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml`\n110:   - Add: `identity.name: agentcube-code-interpreter`\n111:   - Add: `identity.author: agentcube`\n112:   - Add: `identity.label` with multilingual strings (human + llm)\n113:   - Add: `identity.description` with multilingual strings (human + llm)\n114:   - Verify: All identity fields present\n115: \n116: - [ ] **T4.3** Define router_url parameter\n117:   - Add parameter block for `router_url`:\n118:     - `type: string`\n119:     - `required: true`\n120:     - `form: form`\n121:     - `label` and `human_description` and `llm_description`\n122:   - Verify: Parameter complete\n123: \n124: - [ ] **T4.4** Define workload_manager_url parameter\n125:   - Add parameter block for `workload_manager_url`:\n126:     - `type: string`\n127:     - `required: true`\n128:     - `form: form`\n129:     - `label` and `human_description` and `llm_description`\n130:   - Verify: Parameter complete\n131: \n132: - [ ] **T4.5** Define language parameter (optional select)\n133:   - Add parameter block for `language`:\n134:     - `type: select`\n135:     - `required: false`\n136:     - `form: llm`\n137:     - `options: [python, javas