{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886534587,"sessionID":"ses_284ea81b3ffenp7fNy7ULyxuaz","part":{"id":"prt_d7b160290001tkkdD3GPfr0C1O","messageID":"msg_d7b15f34d001lxfydN74g9ClcG","sessionID":"ses_284ea81b3ffenp7fNy7ULyxuaz","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_718ff0a0b50c460bbbef4027","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: identity:\n2:   name: agentcube-code-interpreter\n3:   author: agentcube\n4:   label:\n5:     human:\n6:       en_US: AgentCube Code Interpreter\n7:       ja_JP: AgentCube コードインタープリター\n8:       zh_Hans: AgentCube 代码解释器\n9:       pt_BR: Interpretador de Código AgentCube\n10:     llm:\n11:       en_US: Code execution tool for Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript in Kubernetes sandboxes\n12:       ja_JP: Kubernetes サンドボックスでの Python、JavaScript、TypeScript のコード実行ツール\n13:       zh_Hans: 在 Kubernetes 沙箱中执行 Python、JavaScript 和 TypeScript 代码的工具\n14:       pt_BR: Ferramenta de execução de código Python, JavaScript e TypeScript em sandboxes Kubernetes\n15:   description:\n16:     human:\n17:       en_US: Execute code and commands in secure sandboxed environments with file upload/download capabilities\n18:       ja_JP: ファイルのアップロード/ダウンロード機能を備えた安全なサンドボックス環境でコードやコマンドを実行\n19:       zh_Hans: 在具有文件上传/下载功能的安全沙箱环境中执行代码和命令\n20:       pt_BR: Execute código e comandos em ambientes sandbox seguros com recursos de upload/download de arquivos\n21:     llm:\n22:       en_US: Use this tool to execute Python, JavaScript, or TypeScript code in isolated Kubernetes sandbox environments. Supports code execution, command execution, file operations, and session management.\n23:       ja_JP: このツールを使用して、分離された Kubernetes サンドボックス環境で Python、JavaScript、TypeScript のコードを実行します。コード実行、コマンド実行、ファイル操作、セッション管理をサポートします。\n24:       zh_Hans: 使用此工具在隔离的 Kubernetes 沙箱环境中执行 Python、JavaScript 或 TypeScript 代码。支持代码执行、命令执行、文件操作和会话管理。\n25:       pt_BR: Use esta ferramenta para executar código Python, JavaScript ou TypeScript em ambientes sandbox Kubernetes isolados. Suporta execução de código, execução de comandos, operações de arquivo e gerenciamento de sessão.\n26: parameters:\n27:   - name: router_url\n28:     type: string\n29:     required: true\n30:     form: form\n31:     label:\n32:       en_US: Router URL\n33:       ja_JP: ルーター URL\n34:       zh_Hans: 路由器 URL\n35:       pt_BR: URL do Roteador\n36:     human_description:\n37:       en_US: Base URL of the AgentCube router service\n38:       ja_JP: AgentCube ルーターサービスのベース URL\n39:       zh_Hans: AgentCube 路由器服务的基础 URL\n40:       pt_BR: URL base do serviço do roteador AgentCube\n41:     llm_description: The base URL of the AgentCube router service for code execution requests\n42:   - name: workload_manager_url\n43:     type: string\n44:     required: true\n45:     form: form\n46:     label:\n47:       en_US: Workload Manager URL\n48:       ja_JP: ワークロードマネージャー URL\n49:       zh_Hans: 工作负载管理器 URL\n50:       pt_BR: URL do Gerenciador de Carga de Trabalho\n51:     human_description:\n52:       en_US: Base URL of the AgentCube workload manager service\n53:       ja_JP: AgentCube ワークロードマネージャーサービスのベース URL\n54:       zh_Hans: AgentCube 工作负载管理器服务的基础 URL\n55:       pt_BR: URL base do serviço do gerenciador de carga de trabalho AgentCube\n56:     llm_description: The base URL of the AgentCube workload manager service for session creation and management\n57:   - name: language\n58:     type: select\n59:     required: false\n60:     form: llm\n61:     options:\n62:       - value: python\n63:         label: python\n64:       - value: javascript\n65:         label: javascript\n66:       - value: typescript\n67:         label: typescript\n68:     label:\n69:       en_US: Programming Language\n70:       ja_JP: プログラミング言語\n71:       zh_Hans: 编程语言\n72:       pt_BR: Linguagem de Programação\n73:     human_description:\n74:       en_US: \"Programming language for code execution (default: python)\"\n75:       ja_JP: \"コード実行のプログラミング言語 (デフォルト：python)\"\n76:       zh_Hans: \"代码执行的编程语言 (默认：python)\"\n77:       pt_BR: \"Linguagem de programação para execução de código (padrão: python)\"\n78:     llm_description: The programming language to use for code execution. Choose from python, javascript, or typescript\n79:   - name: code\n80:     type: string\n81:     required: false\n82:     form: llm\n83:     label:\n84:       en_US: Code\n85:       ja_JP: コード\n86:       zh_Hans: 代码\n87:       pt_BR: Código\n88:     human_description:\n89:       en_US: Source code to execute in the sandbox\n90:       ja_JP: サンドボックスで実行するソースコード\n91:       zh_Hans: 在沙箱中执行的源代码\n92:       pt_BR: Código-fonte a ser executado na sandbox\n93:     llm_description: The source code to execute in the sandbox environment\n94:   - name: command\n95:     type: string\n96:     required: false\n97:     form: llm\n98:     label:\n99:       en_US: Command\n100:       ja_JP: コマンド\n101:       zh_Hans: 命令\n102:       pt_BR: Comando\n103:     human_description:\n104:       en_US: Shell command to execute in the sandbox\n105:       ja_JP: サンドボックスで実行するシェルコマンド\n106:       zh_Hans: 在沙箱中执行的 Shell 命令\n107:       pt_BR: Comando de shell a ser executado na sandbox\n108:     llm_description: A shell command to execute in the sandbox environment\n109:   - name: session_id\n110:     type: string\n111:     required: false\n112:     form: llm\n113:     label:\n114:       en_US: Session ID\n115:       ja_JP: セッション ID\n116:       zh_Hans: 会话 ID\n117:       pt_BR: ID da Sessão\n118:     human_description:\n119:       en_US: Existing session ID to reuse (optional)\n120:       ja_JP: 再利用する既存のセッション ID（オプション）\n121:       zh_Hans: 要重用的现有会话 ID（可选）\n122:       pt_BR: ID de sessão existente para reutilizar (opcional)\n123:     llm_description: An existing session ID to reuse for code execution, enabling stateful interactions\n124:   - name: session_reuse\n125:     type: boolean\n126:     required: false\n127:     form: llm\n128:     label:\n129:       en_US: Reuse Session\n130:       ja_JP: セッションを再利用\n131:       zh_Hans: 重用会话\n132:       pt_BR: Reutilizar Sessão\n133:     human_description:\n134:       en_US: \"Whether to reuse an existing session (default: false)\"\n135:       ja_JP: 既存のセッションを再利用するかどうか (デフォルト：false)\n136:       zh_Hans: 是否重用现有会话 (默认：false)\n137:       pt_BR: \"Se deve reutilizar uma sessão existente (padrão: false)\"\n138:     llm_description: Boolean flag indicating whether to reuse an existing session for stateful code execution\n139:   - name: code_interpreter_id\n140:     type: string\n141:     required: false\n142:     form: llm\n143:     label:\n144:       en_US: Code Interpreter ID\n145:       ja_JP: コードインタープリター ID\n146:       zh_Hans: 代码解释器 ID\n147:       pt_BR: ID do Interpretador de Código\n148:     human_description:\n149:       en_US: Specific code interpreter instance ID to use (optional)\n150:       ja_JP: 使用する特定のコードインタープリターインスタンス ID（オプション）\n151:       zh_Hans: 要使用的特定代码解释器实例 ID（可选）\n152:       pt_BR: ID de instância específica do interpretador de código a ser usado (opcional)\n153:     llm_description: A specific code interpreter instance ID to use for execution\n154: extra:\n155:   python:\n156:     source: tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py\n\n(End of file - total 156 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"identity:\n  name: agentcube-code-interpreter\n  author: agentcube\n  label:\n    human:\n      en_US: AgentCube Code Interpreter\n      ja_JP: AgentCube コードインタープリター\n      zh_Hans: AgentCube 代码解释器\n      pt_BR: Interpretador de Código AgentCube\n    llm:\n      en_US: Code execution tool for Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript in Kubernetes sandboxes\n      ja_JP: Kubernetes サンドボックスでの Python、JavaScript、TypeScript のコード実行ツール\n      zh_Hans: 在 Kubernetes 沙箱中执行 Python、JavaScript 和 TypeScript 代码的工具\n      pt_BR: Ferramenta de execução de código Python, JavaScript e TypeScript em sandboxes Kubernetes\n  description:\n    human:\n      en_US: Execute code and commands in secure sandboxed environments with file upload/download capabilities\n      ja_JP: ファイルのアップロード/ダウンロード機能を備えた安全なサンドボックス環境でコードやコマンドを実行\n      zh_Hans: 在具有文件上传/下载功能的安全沙箱环境中执行代码和命令\n      pt_BR: Execute código e comandos em ambientes sandbox seguros com recursos de upload/download de arquivos","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml","time":{"start":1775886534569,"end":1775886534585}}}}
