{"type":"text","timestamp":1775886549751,"sessionID":"ses_284ea81b3ffenp7fNy7ULyxuaz","part":{"id":"prt_d7b161c3a00170ji9O0YJJadwO","messageID":"msg_d7b1607ef001kWZ7Dn1bt8Ps0P","sessionID":"ses_284ea81b3ffenp7fNy7ULyxuaz","type":"text","text":"## AR-036 — Dify 插件集成 Archive\n\n### Completed ✅\n\n**Phase 1: Plugin Bootstrap and Entry Point**\n- `main.py` - Plugin entry point running `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()`\n- `requirements.txt` - Dependencies: `dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0`, `agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10`\n- `.difyignore` - Common ignore patterns\n\n**Phase 2: Plugin Manifest**\n- `manifest.yaml` - Complete with:\n  - Version 0.0.2, type plugin, author volcano-sh\n  - Multilingual labels/descriptions (en_US, ja_JP, zh_Hans, pt_BR)\n  - Icon resources (icon.png, icon-dark.png)\n  - Resource permissions (tool, storage enabled)\n  - Tool provider registration\n  - Meta section (Python 3.12, amd64/arm64)\n  - Optional metadata (created_at, privacy, repo, verified)\n\n**Phase 3: Tool Provider Descriptor**\n- `provider/agentcube.yaml` - Identity, tools list, Python source entry\n\n**Phase 4: Tool Parameter Schema**\n- `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml` - All 8 parameters:\n  - Required: `router_url`, `workload_manager_url`\n  - Optional: `language` (select: python/javascript/typescript), `code`, `command`, `session_id`, `session_reuse`, `code_interpreter_id`\n\n**Phase 5: Provider Implementation**\n- `provider/agentcube.py` - `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider` class with `_validate_credentials()` method\n\n**Phase 6: Tool Implementation**\n- `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py` - `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool` class with `_invoke()` and `execute()` methods\n\n**Phase 7: Documentation**\n- `README.md`, `GUIDE.md`, `PRIVACY.md`\n- Icon files: `icon.png`, `icon-dark.png`\n\n**Phase 8: Verification**\n- Tests directory with `tests/test_plugin.py`\n- All YAML files parse successfully\n- Python modules import correctly\n\n---\n\n### Deferred ⏸️\n\n**None documented** - All 20 acceptance criteria marked complete in tasks.md. Stage ST-3 (Implementation complete) achieved.\n\n---\n\n**Notes:**\n- Plugin follows Dify plugin conventions\n- Uses dify-plugin framework v0.4.x\n- Supports Python, JavaScript, TypeScript code execution\n- Kubernetes sandbox-based execution\n- Session management supported\n- File operations documented (upload/download)","time":{"start":1775886549749,"end":1775886549749}}}
